description: Navigate to Forrest Road. The route begins at a busy intersection, crossing the street towards the corner with the Maycheelin Asian Market. From there, it turns right to proceed along Forrest Road, passing landmarks such as The Doctors pub and a Premier store. The path continues straight down the cobblestone street, ending near a bus stop outside Namaste Kathmandu.
agent_refined_route: Cross the intersection -> Turn Right onto Forrest Road [88m]
